data.description: GORGEOUS, TURN-KEY FURNISHED, LAKEFRONT END UNIT TOWNHOME in DEEP CREEK with 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, A NEW ROOF, and lovely features, awaits new owners! Inside, find a large open floor plan with NEW luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, NEW CABINETS & QUARTZ COUNTERS, NEW LIGHTING, & NEW FURNITURE in this open concept living space with the kitchen connected to the living room and enclosed Florida room on the first level, ALL overlooking the stunning lake view with direct access out to the ground floor, private backyard and lake. Also on this level, find a conveniently located laundry closet and remodeled 1/2 bath, as well as sliding glass doors that can be closed or left open to the Florida Room with extra storage. Upstairs, find a large owners suite with dual closets, and an en-suite bathroom great counter space and shower and a private balcony overlooking the lake with NEW IMPACT FRENCH DOORS with in-glass blinds. Also upstairs, the second bedroom also has an en-suite bathroom with tub/shower combo. This home is being sold turn-key furnished, with STUNNING finishes and has everything you need to just move right in! Enjoy SWFL living with the community pool nearby, a public golf course just around the corner, and great parks, walking paths, shopping, restaurants, access to I-75 and more! Schedule your showing today!
